<style type="text/css">
  h1.mail-title{
    margin:0;
    background-color:#351d09;
    color:white;
    padding:10px 20px;
  }
  h1.welcome-title{
    font-size:40px;
    color:#1e543e;
    margin-top:0;
  }
  .main-section{
    position: relative;
    width: 100%;
    height:auto;
    background-position: center;
    -webkit-background-size: cover;
    -moz-background-size: cover;
    background-size: cover;
    -o-background-size: cover;
    background-image: url("https://s3.amazonaws.com/rails-textbook/rails_for_sfc/images/header/coffee_header3.jpg");
  }
  .main-section-inner{
    background-color:rgba(255, 255, 255, .4);
    padding:30px;
    min-height: 200px;
    text-align:center;
  }
  footer{
    text-align:center;
    color: #777;;
  }
  /* common */
  hr{
    margin-top: 20px;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
    border: 0;
    border-top: 1px solid #ddd;
  }
  .red-hr{
    border-color: #FF3300;
    border-width: 3px;
    width:50px;
    opacity:.5;
  }
  .button {
    display: inline-block;
    width: 200px;
    height: 54px;
    text-align: center;
    text-decoration: none;
    line-height: 30px;
    outline: none;
    background-color: #1e543e;
    border: 2px solid #1e543e;
    color: #fff;
    line-height: 50px;
    transition: all .5s;
  }
  .button:hover{
    background-color: #fff;
    border-color: #1e6439;
    color: #1e6439;
    font-weight:700;
    transition: all .5s;
  }
  .button::before,
  .button::after {
    position: absolute;
    z-index: -1;
    display: block;
    content: '';
  }
  .button,
  .button::before,
  .button::after {
    -webkit-box-sizing: border-box;
    -moz-box-sizing: border-box;
    box-sizing: border-box;
    -webkit-transition: all .3s;
    transition: all .3s;
  }
</style>
<a href="http://coffee-cup.jp" style="text-decoration: none;">
<h1 class="mail-title">
  <img src="https://s3.amazonaws.com/rails-textbook/rails_for_sfc/images/logo/mugcup_logo_link.png" style="height:50px; vertical-align:middle">
  <span class="mail-title-word">Coffee-Cup</span>
</h1>
</a>
<div class="main-section">
  <div class="main-section-inner">
      <h1 class="welcome-title">你好 <%= @resource.family_name %> <%= @resource.first_name %>！</h1>
      <hr class="red-hr">
      <h4>我們受到改變密碼的申請。<br>按下面的按鈕之後，可以改變密碼。</h4>
      <%= link_to '改變密碼', edit_password_url(@resource, reset_password_token: @token), :class => "button" %>
      <hr>
      <h4 class="text-muted">
      ※　如果對這個郵件沒有印象的話，請刪除這郵件。
      <br>
      リンクをクリックしない限り、パスワードは変更されません。
      按了按鈕之後，您的密碼會改變。
      </h4>
  </div>
</div>
<hr>
<footer>
  <small>
  Made by <strong><a href="http://www.coffee-cup.co.jp">Coffee-Cup inc.</a> ・ <a href="http://coffee-cup.jp">Our Page</a></strong>
  <br>
  If you have any questions, contact us ! <a href="mailto:support@coffee-cup.info"><strong><u><strong>support@coffee-cup.info</u></strong></a>
  </small>
</footer>